rows.name: LIST_QST101807仮実装

rows.label: qst101807_msg002
rows.name: ジゾーが借金返すも

rows.label: qst101807_msg003
rows.name: インヴィディアにお金を埋めたも

rows.label: qst101807_msg004
rows.name: 一緒に行く

rows.label: qst101807_msg0001
rows.name:
So, have you got the 500 grand? Or a
nice bit of Divine Beast Quartz?

rows.label: qst101807_msg0002
rows.name: Which will you pay with?

rows.label: qst101807_msg0003
rows.name: Pay with cash

rows.label: qst101807_msg0004
rows.name: Pay with Divine Beast Quartz

rows.label: qst101807_msg0005
rows.name:
It'sokay, dearie... No rush. Just make
sure you pay me before you die.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0006
rows.name:
Thanks for that, dearie. You're free to
go now.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0101
rows.name: Wahehey! Welcome back, Vahsah!

rows.label: qst101807_msg0102
rows.name:
Looks like my partying days are
over for now... But at least we
can leave town.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0103
rows.name: Thanks to friends for help.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0104
rows.name:
Jizo must ask one last little favor,
though.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0105
rows.name:
Please be with Jizo and Vahsah
when meet Possah back in Hræsvelgr.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0106
rows.name:
If Possah still not recognize Jizo,
Jizo probably consumed with
so much despair...

rows.label: qst101807_msg0107
rows.name:
Vahsah maybe end up as Core Crystal
again after all!

rows.label: qst101807_msg0108
rows.name:
Hahah. Jizo's head over heels
in love with Possah, you know.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0109
rows.name:
If she doesn't even recognize him...
yeah, he might just drop dead.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0110
rows.name:
L-l-l-l-l-love?! Jizo not know
about anything like that!

rows.label: qst101807_msg0111
rows.name:
Anyway, if Jizo drop dead...
Will friends take Vahsah?

rows.label: qst101807_msg0112
rows.name:
Thank you much!
Jizo know can count on friends.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0113
rows.name:
Don't I get a say in all this...? Well, I
guess I wouldn't remember anyway.

rows.label: qst101807_msg0114
rows.name:
Now, time to go to village
and see Possah!
